{"tid":474095,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel 決定封殺 UEFI 兼容模式，Win7 將不能開機","createTime":"2017-11-20T00:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T03:15:26.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"170580596d52d5ec29b5ab2f661c9b98706a892a","tid":474095,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T00:09:51.000Z","msg":"目前大多數的電腦都已經採用 UEFI 代替 BIOS，但在作業系統層面上，只有 Windows 8 後才正式支援原生 UEFI，Windows 7 或之前的作業系統，會以 UEFI 中的 CSM(Compatibility Support Module)及Secure Boot 啟動 Legacy 兼容模式，藉此啟動 Windows 7。不過，Intel 研究員 Brian Richardson 在台灣的一場 UEFI 活動中，透露 Intel 決定在 2020 年起，全面停止 UEFI 的 BIOS 兼容性，換言之日後搭載 UEFI 的電腦 (佔新機 9 成以上)，將無法以上述模式啟動 Windows 7 或以前的作業系統。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1950000/1950433/1006web7401_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1950000%2F1950433%2F1006web7401_1024.jpg&h=14828271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1950433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1950433&d=T9%2Fd3cii%2FhqBkXIVL78ZKr5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=b23bfb69\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1950433</a></div>"},{"pid":"fdb35420daa18c68bdb8de1c8a15e2cb94eabfd5","tid":474095,"uid":65400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T00:11:01.000Z","msg":"2020"},{"pid":"7a5db18c883bd01a9dd185a9515ba0ae8062ec91","tid":474095,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:24:07.000Z","msg":"linux呢？"},{"pid":"43b084f2b99df6d9e461749e26b999c8b311eeab","tid":474095,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:25:16.000Z","msg":"收咗m$錢"},{"pid":"34363ec183ad058ad8a2b8f31c27afcd58c240c7","tid":474095,"uid":28563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"ci